        <obo:IAO_0000115>Executive Order 14265, &apos;Modernizing Defense Acquisitions and Spurring Innovation in the Defense Industrial Base&apos; (9 April 2025) -- the executive order directing a comprehensive reform of the Department of Defense&apos;s acquisition processes for speed, flexibility, and execution; the directing instrument for the 2025 Defense Acquisition System reform. Source: Daily Compilation of Presidential Documents, DCPD-202500458.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <dcterms:date>2025-04-09</dcterms:date>
        <dcterms:title>Modernizing Defense Acquisitions and Spurring Innovation in the Defense Industrial Base</dcterms:title>
